tafsir[5]{c,v,t}:
  15,71,"Annabi Luutu maakani ɓe himo ngantinanoo hoore-makko yesso hoɓɓe ɓen: Ɓee ɗoo ko jiwɓe am jeyaaɓe e reseteeɓe mon. Resee ɓe si wonii ko ittugol tuuyu faandiɗon."
  15,73,"Sowto haacaango ngon halkiri ɓe ka puɗal naange."
  15,78,"Gomɗii yimɓe Su'aybu ɓen yimɓe fitaare fiiltiinde kadi ko tooñunirnooɓe yeddugol Alla fenna Nulaaɗo Makko on Su'aybu (yo o his)."
  15,82,"Hari hiɓe taƴiraynoo pelle ɗen fii mahugol cuuɗi ka ɓe hoɗira daɗugol ko ɓe huli."
  15,83,"Haacaango lepte ngon nanngiri ɓe ka subaka."